---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { team } from "../data/content";
---

<Base title="Meet the Team">
  <h1>Meet the Team</h1>
  <p class="label">Three friends. One question. Countless conversations.</p>

  <div class="prose intro">
    <p>
      We're three high school students who share an interest in technology,
      video games, and studying. We started Project Cognify with one
      observation, but it's grown into more through careful research,
      collaboration, and a willingness to fight our own assumptions.
    </p>
    <p>
      While each of us contributes in different ways, every major decision is
      made together. From coming up with ideas to reviewing research, running
      surveys, and building our product, it would be impossible to imagine Project Cognify as is without any of us.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="members">
    {
      team.map((member) => (
        <article class="member">
          <div class="member__body">
            <p class="member__head">
              <span class="member__name">{member.name}</span>
              <span class="member__role">{member.role}</span>
            </p>
            {member.bio.map((para) => (
              <p class="member__bio">{para}</p>
            ))}
            <blockquote class="member__quote">“{member.quote}”</blockquote>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))
    }
  </div>

  <section class="prose believe">
    <h2>What We Believe</h2>
    <p>Project Cognify isn't about proving we're right.</p>
    <p>
      It's about asking better questions, following the evidence, and building
      something that could help students.
    </p>
    <p>We're excited to see what's next.</p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .intro {
    margin: 2.5rem 0 3.5rem;
  }

  .members {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3.5rem;
  }

  .member {
    max-width: 40rem;
  }

  .member__body {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .member__head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .member__name {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .member__role {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
  }

  .member__bio {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
  }

  .member__quote {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--foreground);
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
  }

  .believe {
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    padding-top: 2.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

</style>
